AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020093> "A 'portion of vanadium' is a 'portion of pure chemical element' that 'consists of' only chebi:vanadium atom."@en)
EquivalentClasses(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020093> ObjectIntersectionOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020140> ObjectAllValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000051> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/CHEBI_27698>)))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020093> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0020140>)

