AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000054> "range of motion specification"@en)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000054> "Range of motion is a device specification of  fatigue testing machine which defines ..."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000054> <https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0060006>)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000054> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001938> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0001933>))
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000054> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(ObjectInverseOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/co/PMD_0001026>) <https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000057>))

