AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> <https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000100> "Motor of a fatigue testing machine is a part of such machine which is essential for the applicaiton of loading on a sample."@en)
SubClassOf(<https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000100> <https://w3id.org/pmd/distel/DISTEL_0000057>)
